Feature: Recently Viewed Products
  A list of the last products whose details were reviewed by the current user is displayed by selecting the Recently Viewed Products
Background:
Given I am logged on to the base Url
  And the Administrator has enabled the function to be available to the current user

Scenario: User can access Recently Viewed Products
  Given I click on Recently Viewed Products
  And I can place an order from this link
  Then the link opens the required product to view the product details and all the options from here

